    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are enjoying Railroad Corporation 2 and you want to support us further during the Early Access period, the Subzero Supporter Pack is for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not only is it a great - and warmly appreciated - way for you to support us, it’ll also give you access to exclusive content and perks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Exclusive Art</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/b8940c5ac6e85b0539e08023cc21a665.poster.avif?t=1751040537\" width=698 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/b8940c5ac6e85b0539e08023cc21a665.webm?t=1751040537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/b8940c5ac6e85b0539e08023cc21a665.mp4?t=1751040537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/4c8786c6655a9fb6abbd58f84205f5fb.avif?t=1751040537\" width=640 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Four In-Game Main Menu Backgrounds</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...experience stunning visuals with new Main Menu backgrounds....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/52d7e40e258bfdbbc0ddef98c211582a.avif?t=1751040537\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras_big/52d7e40e258bfdbbc0ddef98c211582a.avif?t=1751040537 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Corporate Top Managers with a Special Skill Set!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/d695651f6ca90c48627341353654a330.avif?t=1751040537\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras_big/d695651f6ca90c48627341353654a330.avif?t=1751040537 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a campaign accompanied by one of the two exclusive top managers available in the DLC. Each of the characters has a special skills set that will make the game experience more unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/d889ddd59184d3b9b495e034671f0f65.webp?t=1751040537\" width=629 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Subzero Supporter Pack DLC also contains two additional in-game music tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Four Unique Portraits for Multiplayer Sessions</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/7d1c4b9e4f82606aea41ca91cbb3f966.avif?t=1751040537\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras_big/7d1c4b9e4f82606aea41ca91cbb3f966.avif?t=1751040537 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283470/extras/edf6499e6b71edfe51a89e8bdaaf7ea6.webp?t=1751040537\" width=640 height=45 /></span>Experience Railroad Corporation 2 like never before with this Supporter Pack which will expand your empire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Our heartfelt thanks</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br>Above all this is a Supporter Pack, and we’re eternally grateful for your care and love. Thank you for showing your support to the team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong> <br>- 4 exclusive Main Menu backgrounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2 exclusive managers with their skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4 exclusive multiplayer portraits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2 additional in-game music scores</p>",
